<Content_wSideColumn ID="x57967" Name="Job Search and Networking Resources" Layout="byuidefault.xsl"><Title type="string" label="Title" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="true">Job Search and Networking Resources</Title><Abstract type="string" label="Abstract" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="true">Home page for internship, job, and career finding resources.</Abstract><xPower Type="GroupStart" GroupStart="" Name="SideColumn" label="L/R Column" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Expanded="false"><MoveLeft type="boolean" label="Toggle column right or left (right is default)" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false">false</MoveLeft><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="ImageComponent" label="Image Component" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="LeftColumnImageComponent"/><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="TextComponent" label="Text Component" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="ColumnTextComponent"/><fbookTop type="boolean" label="Put facebook at top of page" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false">false</fbookTop><fbookStatus type="string" label="Facebook ID#" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false"></fbookStatus><fbookToken type="string" label="Access_Token" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false"></fbookToken><fbookDisplayed type="string" label="Number of facebook messages to display" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false">1</fbookDisplayed></xPower><BodyCopy type="dhtml" label="Body Copy" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false"><![CDATA[<p>If you're ready to start looking for a job, internship, or to start your career, this section will help you with all your needs. Click on the links below or at left to start.</p>
<hr />
<div style="height: 160px;"><a href="x32151.xml" title="Learn more about Career Navigator"><img alt="Career Navigator" height="130" src="Images/advising/jobsearch/careernavigator.jpg" style="float: left; margin-right: 10px;" title="Career Navigator" width="130" /></a>
<h3 style="padding-top: 10px;"><a href="x32151.xml" title="Career Navigator">Career Navigator</a></h3>
<p style="padding-top: 10px;">Career Navigator is a tool available to assist BYU-Idaho students in  their search for internships and career opportunities. Create a profile, upload your job-searching documents, apply for positions online, find career preparation workshops, etc.</p>
</div>
<hr style="clear: left; position: relative; top: 15px;" />
<div style="height: 160px;"><a href="x30281.xml" title="Learn more about Career Navigator"><img alt="Job Postings" height="130" src="Images/advising/jobsearch/newspaper.jpg" style="float: left; margin-right: 10px;" title="Job Postings" width="130" /></a>
<h3 style="padding-top: 10px;"><a href="x30281.xml" title="Career Navigator">Help Wanted - Local Job Postings</a></h3>
<p style="padding-top: 10px;">Looking for a little extra cash? This page contains odd jobs and tasks listed by local community members who only need a student for a few hours or a few days. You'll find personal service needs like painting a house, helping someone move, raking leaves and yard work, etc.<strong></strong></p>
</div>
<hr style="clear: left; position: relative; top: 15px;" />
<div style="height: 160px;"><a href="x30282.xml" title="Recruiters on Campus"><img alt="On Campus Recruiting" height="130" src="Images/advising/jobsearch/recruiters.jpg" style="float: left; margin-right: 10px;" title="On Campus Recruiting" width="130" /></a>
<h3 style="padding-top: 10px;"><a href="x30282.xml" title="Recruiters on Campus">Recruiters on Campus</a></h3>
<p style="padding-top: 10px;">Companies and organizations are frequently on campus recruiting students for jobs, internships and careers. Visit this page to learn more.</p>
</div>
<hr style="clear: left; position: relative; top: 15px;" />
<div style="height: 160px;"><a href="x28936.xml" title="Job Search Tips"><img alt="Job Search Tips" height="130" src="Images/advising/jobsearch/jobsearchtips.jpg" style="float: left; margin-right: 10px;" title="Job Search Tips" width="130" /></a>
<h3 style="padding-top: 10px;"><a href="x28936.xml" title="Job Search Tips">Job Search Tips</a></h3>
<p style="padding-top: 10px;">Several tips and suggestions to aid you in your search for employment, including where and when to look, and how to determine if a job is right for you.</p>
</div>
<hr style="clear: left; position: relative; top: 15px;" />
<div style="height: 160px;"><a href="x28929.xml" title="Additional Job Search Resources"><img alt="Job Search Resources" height="130" src="Images/advising/jobsearch/laptopstudent.jpg" style="float: left; margin-right: 10px;" title="Job Search Resources" width="130" /></a>
<h3 style="padding-top: 10px;"><a href="x28929.xml" title="Additional Job Search Resources">Additional Job Search Resources</a></h3>
<p style="padding-top: 10px;">A list of online services for job and career searching, including special LDS job search sites, and general sites like Monster, Yahoo Jobs, and several others.</p>
</div>
<hr style="clear: left; position: relative; top: 15px;" />
<div style="height: 160px;"><a href="x28930.xml" title="Networking Tips"><img alt="Networking" height="130" src="Images/advising/jobsearch/network.jpg" style="float: left; margin-right: 10px;" title="Networking" width="130" /></a>
<h3 style="padding-top: 10px;"><a href="x28930.xml" title="Networking Tips">Networking Tips</a></h3>
<p style="padding-top: 10px;">An introduction to the purpose and importance of networking, and several guidlines and suggestions that will help you become an effective networker. Includes how to get started, how to carry meaningful and effective networking conversations, and other general tips.</p>
</div>
<hr style="clear: left; position: relative; top: 15px;" />
<div style="height: 160px;"><a href="x32476.xml" title="Networking Resources"><img alt="Networking Resources" height="130" src="Images/advising/jobsearch/jobsearch.jpg" style="float: left; margin-right: 10px;" title="Networking Resources" width="130" /></a>
<h3 style="padding-top: 10px;"><a href="x32476.xml" title="Networking Resources">Networking Resources</a></h3>
<p style="padding-top: 10px;">Visit this page to learn about resources to help you network. Included are BYU-I specific assets such as the BYU-I Alumni Ambassadors, Discovery Fairs, and Hub Service Missionaries, and off-campus resources such as the BYU Management Society, LinkedIn, and LDS Stakes and institutes.</p>
</div>
